{
  "texts": [
    "This study provides a detailed analysis of the medical reasoning capabilities of DeepSeek R1, revealing both its strengths and limitations in handling complex clinical scenarios.",
    "While the model demonstrates high overall diagnostic accuracy (93%), our in-depth error analysis highlights specific areas where its reasoning leads to errors in clinical assessment see Figure 1 and Tables 3-6.",
    "These findings have several important implications for the development and deployment of LLMs in healthcare.",
    "In this work we evaluated the reasoning of LLMs and highlighted cognitive errors in its reasoning.",
    "There is a speculative nature to this since we assign human error mechanism to an LLM system."
  ]
}